"title": "5211: art",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5211: art",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Skilful, creative work, carried out using a variety of materials. Purposes included decoration, ornamentation and representation of objects of worship, the last of which Scripture firmly condemns.</p>\n<h2>Painting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:10\">EZK 8:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:11-Ezek23:15\">EZK 23:11–23:15</a></p>\n<h2>Decorative panelling</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:5-2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:5–3:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:14-1Kgs6:15\">1KI 6:14–6:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps74:3-Ps74:6\">PSA 74:3–74:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:14\">JER 22:14</a></p>\n<h2>Decoration and ornamentation in gold</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:21-1Kgs6:22\">1KI 6:21–6:22</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:4-2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:4–3:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:31-1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:31–6:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:14-1Kgs10:21\">1KI 10:14–10:21</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:13-2Chr9:20\">2CH 9:13–9:20</a></p>\n<h2>Decoration and ornamentation in ivory</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song5:14\">SNG 5:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:18\">1KI 10:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr9:17\">2CH 9:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:39\">1KI 22:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:8\">PSA 45:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:15\">AMO 3:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos6:4\">AMO 6:4</a></p>\n<h2>Carving and sculpture</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:18\">1KI 6:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:29-1Kgs6:35\">1KI 6:29–6:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:7\">2CH 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps144:12\">PSA 144:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:15-Ezek41:26\">EZK 41:15–41:26</a></p>\n<h2>Engraving</h2>\n<h3>As an artistic skill</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:34-1Kgs7:37\">1KI 7:34–7:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:9-Exod28:12\">EXO 28:9–28:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:15-Exod28:21\">EXO 28:15–28:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod28:36-Exod28:38\">EXO 28:36–28:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:6-Exod39:7\">EXO 39:6–39:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:8-Exod39:14\">EXO 39:8–39:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod39:30-Exod39:31\">EXO 39:30–39:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:31\">1KI 7:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:36\">1KI 7:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:5-2Chr2:7\">2CH 2:5–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr2:13-2Chr2:14\">2CH 2:13–2:14</a></p>\n<h3>Metaphorical references to engraving</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:23-Job19:24\">JOB 19:23–19:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:16\">ISA 49:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:1\">JER 17:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:9\">ZEC 3:9</a></p>\n<h2>Art in the tabernacle</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod26:1\">EXO 26:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:18-Exod25:21\">EXO 25:18–25:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:8\">EXO 36:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod36:35-Exod36:38\">EXO 36:35–36:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:7-Exod37:9\">EXO 37:7–37:9</a></p>\n<h2>Art in the temple</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:48-1Kgs7:50\">1KI 7:48–7:50</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:19-2Chr4:22\">2CH 4:19–4:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:13-1Kgs7:22\">1KI 7:13–7:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:27-1Kgs7:37\">1KI 7:27–7:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:40-1Kgs7:45\">1KI 7:40–7:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr4:11-2Chr4:16\">2CH 4:11–4:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr3:15-2Chr3:17\">2CH 3:15–3:17</a></p>\n<h2>Art associated with idolatry</h2>\n<h3>Forbidden</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:15\">DEU 27:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:3-Exod20:6\">EXO 20:3–20:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:7-Deut5:10\">DEU 5:7–5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:22-Exod20:23\">EXO 20:22–20:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:10-Exod34:17\">EXO 34:10–34:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:4\">LEV 19:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev26:1\">LEV 26:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:16-Deut4:19\">DEU 4:16–4:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:23-Deut4:24\">DEU 4:23–4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:16-Deut29:18\">DEU 29:16–29:18</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of idols and images</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs21:7\">2KI 21:7</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:7\">2CH 33:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:1-Exod32:4\">EXO 32:1–32:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:1-Judg17:6\">JDG 17:1–17:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg18:11-Judg18:31\">JDG 18:11–18:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:1-Isa46:2\">ISA 46:1–46:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:1-Jer50:2\">JER 50:1–50:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:9-Ezek8:12\">EZK 8:9–8:12</a></p>\n<h3>Condemned</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:18\">HAB 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:10-Exod34:14\">EXO 34:10–34:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num33:51-Num33:52\">NUM 33:51–33:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:25-Deut7:26\">DEU 7:25–7:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:1-2Chr34:4\">2CH 34:1–34:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:9-Isa44:20\">ISA 44:9–44:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek7:20-Ezek7:22\">EZK 7:20–7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos13:1-Hos13:3\">HOS 13:1–13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic5:13-Mic5:14\">MIC 5:13–5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Nah1:14\">NAM 1:14</a></p>",
